metadata.query:
SELECT TOP 1000 * 
FROM tagnet_AppointmentSPN_ETA eta
INNER JOIN tagnet_AppointmentSPN_PartnerOrderHeaders headers
ON eta.PartnerPrimaryOrderID = headers.PartnerPrimaryOrderID
